sub_title: Global L&D Lead @ AkzoNobel, Podcast Host and Pro Facilitator.
summary:
L&D leader with a track record of creating end-2-end capability development programs from needs analysis to design, deployment, and impact reporting. 
- Experience with large-scale, multi-location, and multi-channel training delivery.
- Highly experienced facilitator of Problem-Solving, Design Thinking, and Leadership training. 
- High proficiency in L&D technologies and integrations w/ relevant tools in the existing HR ecosystem.
- Passionate about L&D Analytics and return on learning business cases;
- Effective Business Partner to functions and Executive Leadership. 
- Affinity for Agile ways of working and digital project management tools for distributed teams.
- Thriving in challenging team projects and passionate about high-performance team culture.
- Podcast Producer and comfortable user of digital storytelling tools (Video, Audio, visualizations, etc) 
- Occasionally a marathon runner.
